--- !u!114 &536
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 110}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 6583a8c65acc7c1ea0da6a34a63afcc0, type: 3}
  m_Name:
  m_EditorClassIdentifier:
  spikerBubble: {fileID: 49}
  setterBubble: {fileID: 47}
  winIntroSetter:
    dialogueOptions:
    - teamName: Club Sumi
      dialogue:
      - Everything's running smoothly.
      - Not bad. For a warm up.
      - 'Game time. Lets play smart. '
    - teamName: Rensho
      dialogue:
      - You didn’t try to out-shout him this time. Smart.
      - Rensho swings wild. Again.
      - 'Well done. '
    - teamName: Kozuki
      dialogue:
      - Felt good to break Kozuki's rythm.
      - Kozuki's well coordinated - we should try some time.
      - Nice timing out there!
    - teamName: Hinami Kai
      dialogue:
      - 'Good. Lets keep this going. '
      - Hinami's a bit too bold ay?
      - Didn't fall for their tricks this time!
    - teamName: Sunaumi High
      dialogue:
      - Caught their rythm this time. Finally.
      - 'Good match. '
      - Woah, did you just aim your shot?!
    - teamName: Namasito
      dialogue:
      - Bet your brother’s real quiet now!
      - Handled him better than last time.
      - Dont showboat too much...
    - teamName: Aomori West
      dialogue:
      - Guess the new teammate didn’t help him much.
      - Their style is weird. Well handled!
      - 'Aomori''s got some stuff to figure out. '
    - teamName: Tenzio
      dialogue:
      - Matched their tempo!
      - Groovy.
      - Good adjustement at the end.
    - teamName: Ten-Roku
      dialogue:
      - Ten-Roku was a suprisingly balanced team!
      - Woah! That felt good!
      - I can't believe that worked.
    - teamName: Daigan Tech
      dialogue:
      - That loss’s gonna stick with them.
      - The wall crumbles...
      - Daigan never cracks. Till now.
  winIntroSpiker:
    dialogueOptions:
    - teamName: Club Sumi
      dialogue:
      - I'm all warmed up. Lets do this!
      - Sumi's definitely getting better!
      - Ok, warm-up’s done. Now it starts for real.
    - teamName: Rensho
      dialogue:
      - Waha! Rensho sucks!
      - Easy peasy, take that Rensho!
      - Heh - he was not taking that loss well.
    - teamName: Kozuki
      dialogue:
      - Heh - not fast enough!!
      - We should try a quick like Kozuki's...
      - Theyre fast sure -I just happen to be faster ;)
    - teamName: Hinami Kai
      dialogue:
      - They really had me guessing there!
      - All flash, no finish — that’s Hinami Kai for you.
      - Hah! Hinami Kai almost got me with that fake — almost.
    - teamName: Sunaumi High
      dialogue:
      - I'm gonna feel that serve for the next week!
      - Aay, THAT was a match!
      - WAHA - Sunaumi High sucks!
    - teamName: Namasito
      dialogue:
      - Perfect defense, huh? Didn’t look so perfect to me.
      - My brother's gonna bring that one up!
      - Namasito... More like nama-see-ya :0
    - teamName: Aomori West
      dialogue:
      - Waha - new teammate, same result!
      - Guess that floaty guy didn’t save 'em.
      - That combo was weird anyways.
    - teamName: Tenzio
      dialogue:
      - All that jazz — still off-beat ;)
      - Guess the purple phase isn’t over yet.
      - Tenzio ain't got nothing on me!
    - teamName: Ten-Roku
      dialogue:
      - They weren't half bad!
      - AAAY!
      - We gotta play like Ten-Roku!
    - teamName: Daigan Tech
      dialogue:
      - Finally punched through that wall!
      - Can't block THAT!
      - Those guys creep me out...
  winIntrosGenericSetter:
  - 'Improving. Definitely. '
  winIntroGenericSpiker:
  - WAHA! What a match!
  prepSetter:
  - I’ll pretend this was a team decision.
  - You keep flying, I’ll keep fixing
  - Fine. Let’s break the rules a bit.
  - Lets THINK this time.
  - They like patterns. Let’s break ’em.
  - We control the pace, we control the match.
  - If they can’t read us they can’t stop us.
  prepSpiker:
  - Oooh this one's spicy!
  - Okay okay okay—hear me out. We go max power, no mercy.
  - Do you think this’ll help me break the sound barrier?
  - Whatever gets me more air time. I want to live up there.
  - Ooh, nasty!
  - This’ll catch ’em slippin’.
  - I want all the power.
  outroSetter:
    dialogueOptions:
    - teamName: 0
      dialogue:
      - Alright, qualifiers. Let's keep this going.
      - Qualifiers, huh? Let’s make this quick.
      - Warm-up’s over. Let’s do this for real.
      - No pressure... Play good.
    - teamName: 2
      dialogue:
      - Tenzio's smart. Take your time.
      - Let’s keep our cool—let Tenzio burn out first.
      - Tenzio's here. Lets play.
    - teamName: 4
      dialogue:
      - Upper bracket. No room for mistakes now.
      - Upper bracket—let’s prove we belong here.
      - Alright. Upper bracket. No more second chances.
    - teamName: 5
      dialogue:
      - Here we go. Sunaumi High's up next.
      - Sunaumi High's pretty steady - lets try to shake 'em.
    - teamName: 6
      dialogue:
      - Watch out. These guys are adapting.
      - So they’re combining styles now? Bold move.
      - Alright, hybrids. Let’s see if the mix holds.
    - teamName: 7
      dialogue:
      - Alright. Let's give this our all!
      - Shirogane. The last wall.
      - Finals. Let’s play like it.
  outroSpiker:
    dialogueOptions:
    - teamName: 0
      dialogue:
      - Qualifiers? EASY!
      - Hope these guys brought helmets!
      - Qualifiers don't scare me!
    - teamName: 2
      dialogue:
      - Lets smash these Tenzio guys!
      - Been waiting for this one.
      - Tenzio’s next? Perfect. I was getting bored.
    - teamName: 4
      dialogue:
      - Gettin up their now! Lets whoop these guys!
      - Upper bracket, baby. Now it’s real.
      - Playin with the big dogs now!
      - Upper bracket? Kinda has a nice ring to it.
    - teamName: 5
      dialogue:
      - Smell's like the ocean over here...
    - teamName: 6
      dialogue:
      - I heard  a few team's are comboing up! Weird!
      - So they’re fusing styles now? Sweet.
      - Guess the hybrids are showing up. Good — I was getting bored.
    - teamName: 7
      dialogue:
      - Shirogane doesn't know what bouts to hit them!
      - Shirogane, huh? Alright.. let’s finish this.
      - End of the line. Let’s make it loud.
      - Last dance. Let's make this good.
  outroSpikerGeneric:
  - Hah, don’t cool off now — next match starts now!
  - We’re just getting started!
  - I'm ready? I'm very ready.
  - Bring it on!
  outroSetterGeneric:
  - Stay sharp - no choking out there!
  - This match? I want it better.
  - Lets keep this rolling.
